50|$|In 1995, {{she became}} President of the <b>Inuit</b> <b>Circumpolar</b> Conference and was {{involved}} in the setting up of the Arctic Council. She has also worked with the International Institute for Sustainable Development, the Migratory Bird Treaty and on Inuit residential school experience where she helped Inuit in receiving compensation.|$|R
